## Status Transitions

### Valid Status Flows

```
Planning → In Roadmap → Draft → In Review → Active
                                              ↓
                         In Progress ←────────┘
                              ↓
                           Active
                              ↓
                    ┌─────────┴─────────┐
                    ↓                   ↓
              Deprecated           Superseded
                    ↓                   ↓
                    └─────────┬─────────┘
                              ↓
                          Archived
```

### Invalid Transitions

- ❌ `Archived` → Any other status (archived is final)
- ❌ `Draft` → `Archived` (must go through Active first)
- ❌ `Planning` → `Active` (must go through Draft and Review)

### Transition Checklist

When changing status:

- [ ] Update `Status` field in metadata
- [ ] Add date field for new status (e.g., `Deprecated Date:`)
- [ ] Add reason field if applicable
- [ ] Add link to replacement if Superseded
- [ ] Add notice banner at top if Deprecated/Superseded
- [ ] Update INDEX.md with status change
- [ ] Update `Last Updated` timestamp
- [ ] Increment version number

