## INDEX.md Maintenance

### When to Update INDEX.md

**ALWAYS update INDEX.md when:**
- Creating a new document
- Changing a document's status
- Renaming or moving a document
- Archiving a document
- Creating a new subdirectory

### INDEX.md Structure Requirements

Every `/docs/INDEX.md` should include:

#### 1. Document Status Changes Section

Track all status changes for audit trail:

```markdown
## Document Status Changes

| Date | Document | Previous Status | New Status | Reason | By |
|------|----------|-----------------|------------|--------|-----|
| 12-09-2025 | api_v1_reference.md | Active | Superseded | v2 released | @developer |
| 12-01-2025 | old_guide.md | Deprecated | Archived | Grace period ended | @developer |
| 11-15-2025 | new_feature.md | Draft | In Review | Ready for review | @developer |
```

#### 2. Recently Updated Section

```markdown
## Recently Updated (Last 30 Days)

| Document | Updated | Version | Status |
|----------|---------|---------|--------|
| [API Reference](./api/API_REFERENCE.md) | 12-09-2025 | 2.1 | Active |
| [Setup Guide](./getting-started/SETUP.md) | 12-05-2025 | 1.3 | Active |
```

#### 3. Documents by Status Section

```markdown
## Documents by Status

### Active Documents
- [Document 1](./path/doc1.md) - Description
- [Document 2](./path/doc2.md) - Description

### In Progress (Being Implemented)
- [Feature Spec](./specs/feature.md) - Implementation started 12-01-2025

### Draft Documents
- [New Guide](./guides/new.md) - ETA: 12-15-2025

### Deprecated/Superseded (Pending Archive)
| Document | Status | Replacement | Archive Date |
|----------|--------|-------------|--------------|
| [Old API](./api/old.md) | Superseded | [New API](./api/new.md) | 01-15-2026 |
```

### INDEX.md Update Checklist

When modifying INDEX.md:

- [ ] Add/update entry in main document listing
- [ ] Update "Recently Updated" section if within 30 days
- [ ] Add entry to "Document Status Changes" if status changed
- [ ] Update "Documents by Status" section
- [ ] Increment INDEX.md version
- [ ] Update INDEX.md "Last Updated" timestamp

