## File Naming for Version Changes

### When Creating New Versions

**DO NOT create versioned filenames:**
```
❌ api_reference_v1.md
❌ api_reference_v2.md
```

**DO create new document and supersede old:**
```
✅ api_reference.md (v2.0 in metadata)
✅ api_reference_legacy.md (Superseded, archived later)
```

**Or use descriptive names:**
```
✅ api_reference_rest.md (REST API)
✅ api_reference_graphql.md (GraphQL API)
```

### Archive Naming Convention

When archiving, append `_archived_YYYY-MM-DD`:
- Original: `api_reference.md`
- Archived: `archive/api_reference_archived_2025-12-09.md`

